<h2 class="no_toc text-delta" id="table-of-contents">Table of contents</h2>
<hr />
<p>General best practice in programming applies to API AutoFlow.</p>

<p>For example, I/O (input/output) devices such as hard drives are generally slower than the processor.</p>

<p>That is why file read/write takes much longer.</p>

<p>It is better to use a database that is optimized to handle frequent access to data</p>
